# Resize Images

## Python Installation :

``` sh
sudo apt-get install python3
sudo apt-get install python3-pip
pip install --upgrade pip
```
## Resize Images installation :

``` sh
pip install resize-image
```

## Usage :

``` sh
python resize_images.py -d "path/to/directory" -w 150 -h 150
```
